          "date": "2013-01-23 21:20:22.000000000",
          "tz": -480
        },
        "subject": "LU-2669 scripts: Fix module list in lnet script",
        "message": "LU-2669 scripts: Fix module list in lnet script\n\nThe lnet start up script's module list was incorrect causing the\nfollowing command to fail:\n\n   # /etc/init.d/lnet stop\n\nThis patch adds missing modules, and rearranges the order certain\nmodules, to match the current dependencies of Lustre modules.\n\nIn particular, the osc module was moved to match it's reliance on\nlov, and the following modules were added to the list: ofd, mdt,\nosd_zfs, osd_ldiskfs, osp, lod, mdd, fid, and fld.\n\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: I081c5feb89ba83960bdc3ed885193d4c7b7cef93\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
